# No admin means no HKLM DefaultShell, so sshd would drop interactive logins
# into cmd.exe. The wrapper starts PowerShell for interactive sessions and
# passes SSH_ORIGINAL_COMMAND (exec/scp/rsync/sftp requests) through cmd /c
# unchanged. The command MUST start with cmd.exe: pty sessions CreateProcess
# the forced command directly (no shell), which cannot execute a bare .cmd
# file. Restart sshd after changing this.
ForceCommand cmd.exe /c C:\Users\jason.christiansen\GitHub\dotfiles\application_configs\portable_sshd\shell_wrapper.cmd